# Step 8: Detect Modified Files

Compare current file hash with baseline hash.

```python
elif baseline[file_name] != current_hash:
    alert = f"[{datetime.now()}] [ALERT] File Modified: {file_name}"
    print(alert)

    baseline[file_name] = current_hash
```

